        class="col-md-3 pswp-gallery__item"
        data-pswp-src="/portfolio-1.jpg"
        data-pswp-width="1200"
        data-pswp-height="800"
      >
        <a
          href="https://cdn.photoswipe.com/photoswipe-demo-images/photos/2/img-2500.jpg"
